{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=3f2d93b0d4638749a55c3020246e64d0&src=http%3A%2F%2Fg.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fdc54564e9258d1094d3b039ed958ccbf6d814dc6.jpg","summary":"百色学院坐落于中国著名的红色革命圣地百色，前身是建于1938年的广西省立田西师范学校，2006年2月，经教育部批准，右江民族师范高等专科学校获准升格为全日制普通本科院校——百色学院。其至今已经有70多年不间断的办学历史。截止2017年2月，百色学院有东合、澄碧两个校区，占地面积1873.59亩，另有百色市政府在百东新区预留用地1606亩。有20个二级学院、一个继续教育学院、一所附属中学和一所职业中专，43个本科专业、30个专科(高职)专业，涵盖经济学、法学、教育学、文学、理学、工学、农学、管理学、艺术学等9大学科门类。","tags":["综合类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1938","所在地区":"广西壮族自治区百色市中山二路21号","院校隶属":"广西壮族自治区"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=e377ebe3fe0f7b607d7ac5368e63507a&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3316141409%2C3740464912%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=6c5a57bca9b7989a029954297a9fc9a3&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3840880156%2C1069966579%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=ee259b562408df66927ec640f12109ee&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3526747310%2C3903258848%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=e825ff9edda527c9331361d610d6348c&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3692297373%2C910336768%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=6f454cbb4f9e595783a91a44d33ba3ea&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2648515043%2C2718618154%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139